Package: LifemapR
Title: Data Visualisation on 'Lifemap' Tree
Version: 1.1.5
Imports: leaflet, shiny, jsonlite, dplyr, tidyr, leaflet.minicharts, htmltools, rlang, RCurl, fastmatch, arrow
